{"tid":1879041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網傳上海於情人節正式封城 禁止外省人車通行","createTime":"2020-02-14T03:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T05:11:11.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6259f30d1219db2bacbbdb969772f0cb13be73fd","tid":1879041,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎讓中國大陸不得不採取封閉式管理，甚至是封城的方式來阻止疫情擴散，昨（13）網路傳出一張上海上海浦東新區新華村村委會的緊急公告，內容寫著，從2月14日凌晨0時開始，從外省市到上海的人和車輛一律不准進入，這也讓大陸網友稱，上海在情人節正式「封城」了。<br />\n<br />\n截至13日12時，上海新增確診病例2例，兩名病患都是從外地到上海的人，總共確診病例達到315例。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，上海已經在10日採取封閉式管理的措施，整個上海市1萬多個住宅區都實施嚴格的進出口管制，並且針對出入的所有人員進行體溫量測，另外如果在上海沒有明確工作及居住地的人，也會規勸禁止進入上海。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/FncNews/world/114619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffnc.ebc.net.tw%2FFncNews%2Fworld%2F114619&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=59fe7b62\" target=\"_blank\">https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/FncNews/world/114619</a><br />\n<br />\n應該係講哩張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fChumW1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfChumW1.png&h=861d91e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7de2a99925c3b2afa66455b6b0c439a1e5b16de","tid":1879041,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T03:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2dca4e176303f404a4d14e17f8ace1b24aad87","tid":1879041,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話要全面復工"},{"pid":"65748207a396d8f0503bb6b4b48ed9f58b1b6ab8","tid":1879041,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b2dca4e176303f404a4d14e17f8ace1b24aad87","tid":1879041,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/ma